        "TileImage": "$($repository 752053dd-2ab7-4d49-897d-97c957f83083).Image",
        "Description": "Gary Lunn is a high-threat enforcer for the CICADA paramilitary organisation, with reputation for brutality that is well deserved. He grew up in the roughest parts of England, and joined the military at an early age, serving in the special forces before a dishonourable discharge in the early 90s. He joined the Sigma Unit and worked with Scott Sarno as a unit marksman and was involved in classified operations north of Sarajevo. Most recently however, Lunn has been on an extended contract with the Etha corporation, who make use of his skills to ensure that highly sensitive projects never end up in the light of day. As such, he has been assigned to their field laboratory in Sapienza in the final phases of Silvio Caruso&#39;s DNA Virus project.",
